        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Assisting Broadband Connectivity Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the Rural Utilities Service, in administering any broadband or telecommunications program, from determining that a project is ineligible for funding because the project has already received state funding. Further, an applicant for funding under such programs may use funds received from a state program to satisfy any matching requirement.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
